# ============================================================================
# Vendor-private firmware sources (must NOT be committed)
# ============================================================================
# Raw firmware preprocessor outputs that disclose panel vendor part numbers
# (e.g. HQR*, FPC-*, KY*) are kept locally for build/inspection only.
# The publishable distribution uses the vetted `include/axs5106l_firmware.h`
# byte array, which carries no panel vendor identifiers.
*.i
*HQR*
*KY[0-9]*
*FPC-*
